data.description: A beautiful spacious home in a quiet neighborhood overlooking all of what Fort Payne has to offer. 5 bedrooms, 3 baths, formal living and dining areas, den w/gas log fireplace, kitchen w/ bar and lots of natural light, 2-car garage and basement recreation room. Large back deck with a seasonal bluff view! Screened porch accessible from the master bedroom. Newer kitchen countertops. Newer appliances. New LVP flooring in master bedroom. Stone shower in master bath. Fire pit area outside to enjoy with guests on chilly nights. Endless opportunities for this amazing home!
